# GOLEM Demo - GLM-Powered CLI Coding Agent
Output assets/demo.gif
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 800
Set Height 500
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Type "# GOLEM - GLM-Powered CLI Coding Agent"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "golem ask 'write a fibonacci function in Go'"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "# Session management"
Enter
Sleep 300ms

Type "golem"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type ":help"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type ":q"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
